race.comment: TINTAURA (12) has hit the top-five in all three outings this campaign and looks to be on the doorstep of a maiden victory. Gets the services of Moor to navigate from the wide draw and a strong showing would not surprise. ARTISTIC TOUCH (14) put in a career-best performance at the Gold Coast last time out and will be rock-hard fit for this. Can play a major role in the outcome. ZOUMAN ALONG (10) looks ready for the mile journey now and may trouble the judge with any luck in running. ZOUBLIME (9) strips fitter second-up from the spell and is one for the multiples. LUMINIZED (1) is at the races for the first time and any market confidence must be noted.
